          Tablet from game. You become owner of that card, and your
          opponent becomes owner of Bronze Tablet. Exchange is permanent;
          play as interrupt. Opponent can prevent exchange by spending 10
          life; this discards Bronze Tablet. Damage-preventing effects
          cannot counter such loss of life. Bronze Tablet comes into play
          tapped. Remove this card from deck if not playing for ante.

